dct_title_s: National Highways map of the State of Alabama : showing eighteen hundred miles of national highways proposed by the National Highways Association
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and contour lines.   Includes text describing the population to be served by proposed highways at bottom of sheet.   "November 1913."   "Copyrighted October 1915 by the National Highways Association ..."   At head of sheet: "Good Roads Everywhere, four-fold system."
dct_publisher_sm: National Highways Association; M.B. Brown Ptg. & Bdg. Co. (Washington; New York), 1915
